 hinge loss?\r\n\r\nAccording to https://arxiv.org/pdf/1802.05957.pdf equation (17),\r\nV_D = E[min(0, -1+D(real_data))] + E[min(0, -1-D(G(z)))]\r\n\r\nBut in here, it's\r\nrelu(1 + outputs).mean() = max(0, 1 + outputs).mean() ~= E[max(0, 1-D(real_data))] + E[max(0, 1+D(G(z)))]\r\n\r\nI guess there a minus sign should be added to achieve the same behaviour?","closed_by":{"login":"Nash2325138","id":17662095,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3NjYyMDk1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17662095?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138","html_url":"https://github.com/Nash2325138","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Nash2325138/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/knazeri/edge-connect/issues/60/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/knazeri/edge-connect/issues/60/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}